    <title>VMware虚拟机中CentOS7系统网络配置</title>
    <link>https://eebond.github.io/vmware%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%ADcentos7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link>
